data.title: GSK’s Stiefel Adds Psoriasis/Atopical Dermatitis Candidate In Licensing Deal
data.meta_description: For about $34 million, Stiefel gets development and commercialization rights in most of the world to a novel, non-steroidal, topical anti-inflammatory compound in Phase II.
